# Color System

All colors must use CSS variables from `/src/styles/theme.css` or the semantic tokens below. Reference: `/src/imports/SemanticsColorTokens.tsx`.

## Primary Colors
| Token | Hex | Alias | Usage |
|---|---|---|---|
| Background Primary 1 Strong | `#00b8f5` | sky_blue_400 | Brand primary, `var(--primary)` |
| Background Primary 2 Strong | `#004299` | navy_blue_650 | Hyperlinks, CTA buttons |
| Background Primary Weak | `#e0f5fd` | sky_blue_50 | Icon containers, subtle highlights |
| Background Primary Medium | `#b1e6fb` | sky_blue_100 | Sidebar active state |

## Semantic State Colors
| State | Strong | Weak | Weak Usage |
|---|---|---|---|
| Positive (Success) | `#21c179` (green_400) | `#e3f6ec` (green_50) | Status chips, badges |
| Notice (Warning) | `#ff9d00` (orange_700) | `#fff8e1` (orange_50) | P1 cards at 60% opacity |
| Negative (Error) | `#fd5154` (red_400) | `#ffebef` (red_50) | P0 cards at 60% opacity, validation |

## Neutral Colors
| Token | Hex | CSS Variable | Usage |
|---|---|---|---|
| Foreground | `#101010` | `var(--foreground)` | Body text, headings |
| Muted Foreground | `#7e7e7e` | `var(--muted-foreground)` | Labels, descriptions, placeholders |
| Border | `#e0e0e0` | `var(--border)` | Borders, dividers, separators |
| Background | `#ffffff` | `var(--background)` | Page backgrounds |
| Surface Level 3 | `#fafafa` | `var(--surface-level-3)` | Table headers, card sub-sections |
| Offset Weak | `#f5f9fe` | ŌĆö | Search bars, input hover, subtle BG |
| Sidebar BG | `#e7f1f8` | ŌĆö | L1/L2 navigation background |
| Disabled BG | `#ebebeb` | ŌĆö | Disabled buttons, disabled inputs |
| Disabled Text | `#acacac` | ŌĆö | Disabled text content |

## Chart Colors
| Slot | Hex | CSS Variable |
|---|---|---|
| Chart 1 | `#00b8f5` | `var(--chart-1)` |
| Chart 2 | `#21c179` | `var(--chart-2)` |
| Chart 3 | `#ff9d00` | `var(--chart-3)` |
| Chart 4 | `#fd5154` | `var(--chart-4)` |
| Chart 5 | `#fed533` | `var(--chart-5)` |

## Icon Colors
- Container BG: `#e0f5fd` (Primary Weak)
- Icon body/background: `white` (literal `fill="white"`)
- Icon detail: `#101010` via `currentColor` ŌĆö ALL icons use this single dark color
- NEVER use `#004299` or `#00b8f5` inside SVGs ŌĆö those are for links and buttons only

## Rules
- Use semantic color names in documentation, not raw hex
- Opacity via Tailwind `/60` syntax: `bg-[#ffebef]/60`
- Hyperlinks always `#004299`, destructive actions `var(--destructive)`
- Don't mix semantic tokens with arbitrary hex ŌĆö be consistent
- SVG icons MUST use `currentColor` ŌĆö see `icons/icons.mdc`
